PrecisReappointment of ROXANE VACHON of Montréal, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montréal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and her designation as Assistant Deputy Chairperson of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montréal Regional Office), effective May 30, 2021.
